newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 529 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 529 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural contracts trading volume totaled 529 contracts, compared with 765 contracts traded overnight Tuesday.
There were six wheat, 356 corn, 100 soybean, seven soymeal, 58 soyoil, one corn call and one corn put traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was 1/4 to 1/2 cent lower, corn was 1/4 to one cent higher and soybeans were 1/2 lower to 1-1/2 higher.
